    ('BUS-T 375', 'KELLEY COMPASS 3', '6138', 'Closed', NULL, 'WB WEB', 'Katherine Ryan', 0, NULL, 'Discussion', '1', 'WEB-BASED CLASS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Students will continue in the student talent management system by, learning to carry out objectives in face-to-face team meetings as well as virtual meetings. In addition, students will continue to fine-tune resumes to fit their increased awareness of personal goals and improve interview strategies to secure positions with companies with similar goals and values.', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], NULL),
